- No need to tell them.

30
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:02,760
No, you have to.

31
00:03:04,110 --> 00:03:05,780
Did your dad say something?

32
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:16,280
Is it about you and me?

33
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:22,940
I'm already

34
