an adult, after all.

35
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,450
I don't need them nitpicking each
and everything I do.

36
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:34,820
Ugh, seriously.

37
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:37,360
I am so disappointed
about my own parents.

38
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:40,700
He didn't have to be so
over the top about it, did he?

39
00:03:41,090 --> 00:03:42,940
Mom's fine with anything but
dad has always been approving.

40
