Can I open it? Can I see?

66
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:44,610
What? What is this?

67
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:46,890
Knitted sweater!

68
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:50,080
It has "M" on it.

69
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:51,390
"M"!

70
00:04:51,410 --> 00:04:53,560
This here.
- Wait, it's "M" for "Makki", right?

71
00:04:53,580 --> 00:04:55,600
Yes.
- So cute!

72
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:57,710
Good for you. I wonder
what I got?

73
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,520
You're wearing it now?
- Can I?

74
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:01,010
For real?
- What?

75
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:03,270
A scarf?
- A scarf.

76
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:06,900
Really? It's so cute! Thank you!

77
00:05:06,930 --> 00:05:09,070
Looks nice.
- It really suits you.

78
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,300
Right?

79
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,290
I'm so happy.

80
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,420
You're eating the chicken too?

81
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:38,770
Chicken meat for ramen?

82
00:05:38,790 --> 00:05:40,040
Here.

83
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,350
Thanks.
- It's good once cold.

84
