- What are you doing?

378
00:26:40,850 --> 00:26:42,200
Move closer.
- Not again?

379
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:43,180
Alright.

380
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:44,660
I'll send it to Chisa.

381
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:46,990
You guys are so close.
- To Chisa?

382
00:26:47,020 --> 00:26:47,960
Send to Chisa.

383
00:26:49,310 --> 00:26:50,310
Alright.

384
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:53,020
What now?
- Pose!

385
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:57,300
How much more are you
going to take?

386
00:26:58,180 --> 00:26:59,040
What?

387
00:27:00,260 --> 00:27:02,590
Nah.
- Your face is puff red.

